HEADWORD: Lousewort
<hw>Louse"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>Any species of <gen>Pedicularis</gen>, a genus of perennial herbs.
It was said to make sheep that fed on it lousy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Yellow lousewort</b></col>, <cd>a plant of the genus
<gen>Rhinanthus</gen>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lousily</ent>⟦br⟧
